{"tid":1677950,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"心痛，唔好再搞大型遊行得唔得？快閃先係皇道","createTime":"2019-10-27T11:39:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-27T12:44:27.000Z","uid":54303,"like":9,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"71aa7d4f26732e89a946fe146cd2ec418b042003","tid":1677950,"uid":54303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T11:39:25.000Z","msg":"明明我地有更多攻擊目標，點解仲要墨守成規？<br />\n明明班公安係濫捕濫權，點解仲要預早比時間、比地點班畜牲佈陷阱？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n和平遊行每次都會比班撚樣搞到變暴力衝突，每次都有手足被捕，而我地又得到乜野？遊行仲合唔合符成本效益？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我地既示威活動應該日常化、地下化，日常化和理非抗爭，包括經濟抗爭、伏班藍絲同事、勤力air drop等等，勇武抗爭應該搵少數信得過既人組織成小隊，然後不定期快閃打各類目標。<br />\n敵人變招，我地都要變招。最後我想講，大家唔好只係注重班黑警，佢地背後既文官一樣都係罪大惡極。"},{"pid":"1f8547b1eeed10a60a1fb791b39ed0f75d99d44d","tid":1677950,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T11:39:35.000Z","msg":"【黃色經濟】有個傻仔整咗個黃藍商鋪認證平台<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/eqgeNS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/eqgeNS</a><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e00d21cfe6a3f100bbcb5c6b152673e6a05f3b7a","tid":1677950,"uid":54303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T11:41:57.000Z","msg":"番寫字樓既應該要諗方法陰班confirm藍既同事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2609dfb5d2eb76dea9790a188b7ef470d2b773c6","tid":1677950,"uid":73565,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T11:46:51.000Z","msg":"大遊行唔應該有勇武手足<br />\n應該遊行時四圍快閃 兵分兩路"},{"pid":"f36190e2aaf40ee2b7a55b9f09b8d04023691e29","tid":1677950,"uid":54303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T11:48:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"689b62cee27de7a296af3401be3713fa6163ffa3","tid":1677950,"uid":53666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T11:51:12.000Z","msg":"尖沙咀又死城一日<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1677521\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1677521</a><br />\